WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.166 --> 00:00:04.300
So you are the new consort the emperor has appointed.

2
00:00:04.566 --> 00:00:06.600
You do seem somewhat self-centered.

3
00:00:07.900 --> 00:00:11.000
I’ve met the Empress before.

4
00:00:11.100 --> 00:00:12.600
You know me?

5
00:00:13.100 --> 00:00:16.400
Just kidding. Even if we were enemies in a past life,

6
00:00:16.400 --> 00:00:18.866
this life’s love story between you and the dog emperor

7
00:00:18.866 --> 00:00:20.400
is just gossip for the common people.

8
00:00:20.400 --> 00:00:21.500
How could I not know?

9
00:00:22.333 --> 00:00:23.133
Naturally.

10
00:00:23.266 --> 00:00:26.266
The love story between Consort and the Emperor is widely known

11
00:00:26.266 --> 00:00:27.666
and talked about everywhere.

12
00:00:27.666 --> 00:00:29.833
Who doesn’t know about it?

13
00:00:30.466 --> 00:00:32.066
You spoke quite well at the time.

14
00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:33.866
But,

15
00:00:34.400 --> 00:00:37.366
why haven’t you shown any respect upon meeting me?

16
00:00:37.533 --> 00:00:38.366
This is problematic.

17
00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:40.800
I forgot I’m now of lower rank,

18
00:00:40.800 --> 00:00:42.866
after being on equal footing with him for too long.

19
00:00:46.400 --> 00:00:47.933
It’s my first time in the palace.

20
00:00:47.933 --> 00:00:50.633
I’m still not quite familiar with the palace rules.

21
00:00:50.866 --> 00:00:53.433
Why don’t I give you a proper lesson?

22
00:00:53.500 --> 00:00:56.166
How about that?

23
00:00:57.933 --> 00:00:59.366
So accommodating,

24
00:00:59.566 --> 00:01:01.466
unlike his usual demeanor.

25
00:01:04.133 --> 00:01:06.666
Considering we will be sisters in the future,

26
00:01:06.666 --> 00:01:08.366
I won’t make things difficult for you.

27
00:01:08.766 --> 00:01:11.633
How about this: three kneelings and nine kowtows

28
00:01:12.100 --> 00:01:14.233
before my feet,

29
00:01:14.500 --> 00:01:16.800
and I’ll forgive your rudeness.

30
00:01:17.400 --> 00:01:19.000
I knew it.

31
00:01:19.200 --> 00:01:20.600
From now on,

32
00:01:20.600 --> 00:01:22.800
I will never lift my head high in the harem.

33
00:01:22.800 --> 00:01:25.133
This woman will definitely take advantage of this.

34
00:01:25.133 --> 00:01:26.866
She’ll impose even harsher penalties.

35
00:01:27.733 --> 00:01:30.800
It seems Consort Rong is not very willing.

36
00:01:31.066 --> 00:01:32.433
Fuluo Ruofeng,

37
00:01:32.766 --> 00:01:35.900
go help her.

38
00:01:37.933 --> 00:01:39.633
Let go of me!

39
00:01:39.766 --> 00:01:41.000
Let me go!

40
00:01:41.700 --> 00:01:43.600
What sin have I committed?

41
00:01:43.733 --> 00:01:45.200
Not only am I being used as a scapegoat,

42
00:01:45.200 --> 00:01:46.400
but I’m also being subjected to humiliation.

43
00:01:46.966 --> 00:01:48.700
Why don’t those despicable people just die?

44
00:01:48.733 --> 00:01:49.966
Stop this!

45
00:01:51.666 --> 00:01:52.466
Ah!

46
00:01:53.400 --> 00:01:54.200
Ah!

47
00:01:54.733 --> 00:01:56.966
You really have some nerve!
